Local chemicals and energy company Sasol has contracted oil and gas recruitment specialist Petroplan to provide consultancy and managed services in the UK, South Africa and Mozambique. Petroplan already has a long-standing working relationship with Sasol through the provision of both contract and permanent oil and gas professionals in the UK and South Africa. &ldquo;We are delighted to continue supporting Sasol&rsquo;s growth in these regions while offering career opportunities from this industry leader to our qualified candidate network,&rdquo; Petroplan said in a statement on Tuesday.